{"tid":1984431,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"話說我啊姨收到中國親戚嘅電話","createTime":"2020-04-22T12:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T06:14:23.000Z","uid":315016,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5d379055c9b2c8ec202fe53714c559aaae317499","tid":1984431,"uid":315016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:39:37.000Z","msg":"話說我啊姨三十幾年前嫁落黎香港，近排冇聯絡好耐嘅中國親戚無啦啦打俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啊姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:喂，村委打過黎問我拎你電話喎，問你5月1號有冇登記投票<br />\n啊姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:投票？我戶口都唔喺村嗰到，投咩票？<br />\n親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:唔係吖，講緊香港有冇登記投票，香港登記左投票大陸村委呢邊都要你地啲資料喎<br />\n啊姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:咁奇怪，我呢邊投票關大陸咩事，你咪比我啲資料佢<br />\n親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:好好....<br />\n<br />\n真人真事，唔知你地有冇同樣情況，佢叫我放上黎問下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6301815a9110d716f4e1b2b6a6d9e90645df59df","tid":1984431,"uid":315016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7511082e02557ed5adc18fa2020d98d44ecf1ed","tid":1984431,"uid":11156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:40:43.000Z","msg":"下"},{"pid":"f7d3e43feba8d766aa755114717390918958beed","tid":1984431,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ab6c4b4e1e1546b7da2bce50d9f195526af2bb","tid":1984431,"uid":315016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"537f7ff1c25fc901e5a56fa2d95